OL,3,CPSNI breakdown of stalking arrests by
OL,4,Carea
OL,6,FMore than 300 people have been
OL,7,Farrested for alleged stalking offences
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland in two years.JThe
OL,9,FPSNI said between April 2022 and March
OL,10,F31 2024 officers arrested 312 alleged
OL,11,Fstalkers. Of those 150 were charged.
OL,12,FMost of the arrests were made in
OL,13,FBelfast (69), followed by Armagh,
OL,14,FBanbridge and Craigavon (38), Newry,
OL,15,FMourne and Down (34), Derry City and
OL,16,FStrabane (32), Antrim and Newtownabbey
OL,17,F(30), Fermanagh and Omagh (22), while
OL,18,F19 of the arrests were made in both
OL,19,FMid Ulster and Mid and East Antrim.
