OL,8,Fand North Down and 14 in Causeway
OL,9,FCoast and Glens.JAt the start of
OL,10,FNational Stalking Awareness Week, the
OL,11,FPSNI also said that since October
OL,12,F2023, officers have made the first
OL,13,Fsuccessful application for a Stalking
OL,14,FProtection Order to safeguard victims
OL,15,Fand put prohibitions on alleged
OL,16,Fperpetrators' behaviours.JDetective
OL,17,FSuperintendent Lindsay Fisher
OL,18,Fdescribed stalking as an "insidious
OL,19,Fcrime that takes over and destroys
OL,20,Flives".J"We are asking the public to
OL,21,Fnot ignore the red flags. If someone's
